1846418368255908016.Text: Mevure Hlen is a Clothier in the St. Olms section of Vivec. She is apparently unhappy with the high prices of importing materials for her shop. Because of it, she is forced to sell her goods at higher prices than normal.

10663143381253916631.Text: Mevure Hlen suspects that she is being gouged by the East Empire Company, and that they may be artificially inflating prices. She would like me to try and steal a price list from the offices of the East Empire Company in Ebonheart.

1048927648585423741.Text: I have agreed to try and get a price list from the East Empire Company.

171896695179110267.Text: I have agreed to try and get a price list from the East Empire Company. I believe that the package I delivered to J'Zhirr may be exactly what Mevure Hlen is looking for.

2825522740277602813.Text: I have decided not to help Mevure Hlen.

689035951400514032.Text: I have retrieved the price list from J'Zhirr at the East Empire Company and returned it to Mevure Hlen. She was visibly upset by the contents, and vowed to find another supplier for her inventory and immediately lower her prices. Mevure Hlen was right about one thing: I have learned a few things about business, and will be more successful in my business dealings henceforth.
